Package com.hazelcast.spi.merge

Class SplitBrainMergeTypes

java.lang.Object
com.hazelcast.spi.merge.SplitBrainMergeTypes
public class SplitBrainMergeTypes
extends Object
Collection of interfaces which define the provided merge types for each data structure.

Useful for implementors of SplitBrainMergePolicy to check on which data structures their custom merge policy can be configured.

Used by the ConfigValidator to check if a configured SplitBrainMergePolicy is usable on its data structure.

Since:
3.10
